					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Parchment and paper codex; Spanish and Italian semi-cursive script.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="mixed">
								<support>Parchment and paper codex</support>
								<extent>61 folios<dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
										<height>216</height>
										<width>155</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>145</height>
										<width>105</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>61 folios (+ 4 unfoliated flyleaves at the beginning and 4 at the end of the manuscript).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires mostly of 8 leaves.</p>
									<p>Additional 7 paper leaves at the beginning of the manuscript.</p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1 3" ruledLines="29" writtenLines="29">
									<p>Text written in one to three columns, with 24 to 29 columns to a page.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
						<handDesc hands="3">
							<summary>Spanish and Italian semi-cursive script. <name type="person" role="scribe">Mosheh</name>: inscription in a form of acrostic beginning: מזמר ליום שבת עונג ונופש, folio 39r; Italian semi-cursive script of the 15th century.</summary>
							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="major">
								<p>
									<locus from="1r" to="2r"/> Italian/Byzantine semi-cursive of approximately 15th century</p>
								<p>
									<locus from="2v" to="7r"/>Spanish semi-cursive of approximately 15th century</p>
								<p>
									<locus from="8r" to="61v"/>Italian/Byzantine semi-cursive of approximately 15th century</p>
							</handNote>
						</handDesc>
						<decoDesc>
							<summary>Sefirotic tree.</summary>
							<decoNote type="diagram">
								<locus from="8v" to="9r"/>Sefirotic tree, ink drawing with a commentary.</decoNote>
						</decoDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Number of personal notes, written in a later hand, on folio <locus n="">7v:</locus>
								<q>בשנת תל"ב ביום ש"ק שמנה עשר לחדש אלול נפטר לעולמו כבוד א"א ז"ל </q>
							</p>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Barukh Galiko</name>, inscribed with his name on folio 39r: להו': קניתיהו אני ברוך גאליקו מיד כמהח"ר משלם סלם יצ"ו</p>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="censor">Clemente Renatto</name>, his name signed on folio 38v.</p>
						</additions>
